• **Annual Maximum**: $1,000-$2,000

**Northern CA Network:**
• **Dentists**: Extensive network across Northern CA
• **Specialists**: Orthodontists, oral surgeons, etc.
• **Hospitals**: Dental surgery centers
• **Convenience**: Multiple locations

**Cost Considerations:**
