• **Copay**: $20 for most services

**DHMO Features:**
• **Network Only** - Must use designated providers
• **No Referrals** - Direct access to specialists
• **Lower Costs** - Reduced premiums and copays
• **Preventive Focus** - Emphasis on regular checkups

**Typical DHMO Benefits:**
• **Cleanings & Exams**: Usually 100% covered
• **Basic Procedures**: 80-90% coverage
